Eikoo oloiboni le Nkai oji Mikaia Ahab

(
1   Ilai 
22  .
1  -
28  )


1  Eeta Yehoshafat enkarsisisho sapuk o enkanyit neitobir olning'o tenkaraki enkiyama o ltung'ana le Ahab, 
2  ore te siadi ilkuti arin nedoyio alo enetii Ahab te Samaria. Neyiang'aki Ahab ninye nkerra kumok o lmong'i tenebo lelo tung'ana apa ootii tenebo ninye, neilejilej ninye pee epuo aagilunore Ramot-Gilead. 
3  Nejoki Ahab, ilo aiguanani loo Siraeli Yehoshafat olaiguanani le Yuda, “Eilo iyie tenebo nanu Ramot-gilead?” Newal ninye ajo, “Atiu nanu anaa enitiu iyie, netiu iltung'ana laainei anaa iltung'ana linono. Kiaku iyiook tenebo iyie to larrabal.”


4  Neitoki Yehoshafat ajoki olaiguanani loo Siraeli, “Tang'asa nkilikuanishore ororei lo Laitoriani.” 
5  Neitoki olaiguanani loo Siraeli aiturrurr iloibonok le Nkai tenebo, iltung'ana iip ong'uan, nejoki ninche, “Aikipuo iyiook olarrabal aagilunore Ramot-Gilead, anaa aimikipuo?” Nejoki ninche, enchom, amu keishoru Enkai apik nkaik o laiguanani. 
6  Kake etejo ninye Yehoshafat, “Aimeetae likae oiboni le Nkai likinkilikuanishore?” 
7  Nejoki olaiguanani loo Siraeli Yehosafat, “Eton etii oltung'ani obo likindim iyiook aaikilikuanishore tialo Olaitoriani, Mikaia olayioni le Imala; kake manyor nanu ninye, amu meibonu aikata isupati tialo nanu, ntorrok ake eibonu.” Nejo Yehoshafat, mincho olaiguanani ejo neijia.” 
8  Neitoki olaiguanani loo Siraeli aipotu olkitok obo, nejoki, “Iyau nabo kata Mikaia olayioni le Imala.” 
9  Ore ina kata netonita olaiguanani loo Siraeli o Yehoshafat, olaiguanani le Yuda too lorikan le nkitoo, neishopo ilkilani lenye, netonita ninche te wueji neituutishoreki, te mpolos e kishomi e Samaria; neibonisho iloibonok pooki te dukuya ninche. 
10  Ore Sedekia olayioni le Kenaana neitobiraki kewan imowuarak e sekenkei, nejo, “Nji ejo Olaitoriani, ‘Te kuna ilo iyie arrumoo ile Siria o metaba anaa neidak ninche.’ ” 
11  Ore iloibonok pooki neibonu ina, nejo, “Ilepa shomo Ramot-gilead pee ilo amirisho; aikincho iyie Olaitoriani apik enkaina o laiguanani.”


12  Ore lelo kulikae apa ooshomo aaipotu Mikaia nejoki ninye, “Ng'ura ore irorei loo loibonok le Nkai pooki neimaki embae nabo supat tialo olaiguanani; nchoo orerei lino etiu anaa orerei le obo lenye, niro te supatisho.” 
13  Kake etejo Mikaia, “Ore anaa enaishu Olaitoriani, ore ina najo Enkai ai ina nanu airo.” 
14  Ore ake pee ebau enetii olaiguanani, nejoki olaiguanani ninye, “Mikaia, eikipuo iyiook Ramot-gilead, olarrabal anaa aikipal?” Newalu ninye ajo, “Ilepa shomo timirisho; kepiki ninche enkaina ino.” 
15  Kake etiaka olaiguanani ninye, “Aikatitin aja aasai nanu pee iro esipata ake te nkarna o Laitoriani?” 
16   Neitoki ninye ajo, “Atoduaa nanu Isiraeli pooki eidapashakinote ildoinyio anaa nkerra nemeeta olchekut; netejo Olaitoriani, ‘Meeta kulo olaitasheikinoni; nchoo pooki ng'ae errinyo alo enkang enye te seriani.’ ” 
17  Neitoki olaiguanani loo Siraeli ajoki Yehoshafat, “Keitu nanu aajoki iyie nchere meibonu ninye esidai tialo nanu, kake entorroni ake eibonu?” 
18  Nejo Mikaia, “Toning'o naa orerei lo Laitoriani: Atoduaa nanu Olaitoriani etonita to lorika lenye le nkitoo, ore olorora pooki le shumata, neitashe te nkaina enye e tatene, o te ne kedienye. 
19  Nejo Olaitoriani, ‘Aing'ae olo alej Ahab olaiguanani loo Siraeli, pee etum ninye ashomo atabatatayu te Ramot-gilead?’ Nejo obo embae nabo, nejo olikae enkae. 
20  Neitoki alotu enkiyang'et neitashe te dukuya Olaitoriani, ejo, ‘Kalo nanu alej ninye.’ Nejoki Olaitoriani, ‘Tia oitoi?’ 
21  Nejo ninye, ‘Kalo nanu, naaku oltau le lejare too nkutukie oo loibonok lenyena.’ Nejo ninye ilo iyie alej ninye, naa ndimu ninye, shomo naa taasa ina. 
22  Ore naa taata etipika Olaitoriani enkiyang'et e lejare nkutukie e kulo oibonok linono; eiroro entorroni tialo iyie.”


23  Neitoki Sedekia olayioni le Kenaana anyiku neosh Mikaia eseder, nejoki, “Kaji eimua enkiyang'et o Laitoriani pee epuku te nanu nikilotu airorie iyie?” 
24  Nejo Mikaia, “Ng'ura, ilo iyie adol teina olong, tinilo iyie olgilata liatua aisudori.” 
25  Nejo ilo aiguanani loo Siraeli, “Embung'a Mikaia, nirrinyirrinyi ninye aaya enetii Amon ilo balusui le nkanasa, o enetii Yoash ilo ayioni lo laiguanani. 
26  Nilo ajo, ‘Nji ejo olaiguanani, Entipik ena tung'ani atua korokoroni, ninchosho ninye meinosa imukateni naatoito neok enkare, o metaba anaa nashukunye te seriani.’ ” 
27  Nejo Mikaia, “Tenitushukunye iyie te seriani, neitu nanu aairorie Olaitoriani”, neitoki ninye ajo, “Entoning intae lo orere pooki!”

Keeya e Ahab

(
1   Ilai 
22  .
29  -
35  )


28  Neaku eshomo olaiguanani loo Siraeli; o Yehoshafat olaiguanani le Yuda Ramot-gilead. 
29  Nejoki olaiguanani loo Siraeli Yehoshafat, “Kaibelekeny nanu enkishopo ai nalo olarrabal, kake inchopo iyie ilkilani linono le nkitoo.” Neibelekeny olaiguanani loo Siraeli enkishopo enye nepuo ninche olarrabal. 
30  Neitanapa apa olaiguanani le Siria ilkituaak loo ngarrin enyena oo mbartan, ajoki, “Emiarare ake oloti anaa olkitok, kake olaiguanani loo Siraeli ake entaarare.” 
31  Ore ake pee edol lelo kituaak loo ngarrin oo mbartan Yehoshafat nejo ninche, “Olaiguanani loo Siraeli ilo.” Neibelekenya ninche aarare ninye; neyietu Yehoshafat abuaku, neretu Olaitoriani ninye. Neboinaa Enkai ninche aitung'uaa ninye. 
32  Amu etoduaa ake lelo kituaak loo ngarrin oo mbartan aajo mme olaiguanani loo Siraeli ilo nerrinyo te sujata enye. 
33  Kake eteyietuo oltung'ani obo enkawuo enye nengoroo embae, neng'or olaiguanani loo Siraeli eripata enkila enye esekenkei, to lgoo; ore enkaraki ina nejoki ninye olarewani lenye le ngarri e mbarta, “Mbelekenyayu ntung'uayioki nanu olarrabal, amu aatipikaki nanu olbae.” 
34  Neirowuaju oleng olarrabal ina olong, neigarakino olaiguanani loo Siraeli eng'arri enye embarta aing'or ile Siria o metaa teipa. Ore ake pee edoyio enkolong neye.

